29 23-79-2902. Coverage for cognitive assessment.
30 (a) A healthcare insurer that offers, issues, or renews a health
31 benefit plan in this state shall provide coverage for assessment for
32 cognitive function, Alzheimer's disease, or dementia for a patient who is:
33 (1) Sixty (60) years of age or older; or
34 (2) Forty-five (45) years or older and at a higher risk for
35 Alzheimer's disease, dementia, or impaired cognitive function, including
36 without limitation having a family history of dementia, Down Syndrome,
